name: Private Pre-Sale! 11 Day Winter Detox Program
description:
This 11-Day Program is going to change your life forever: You will improve your digestion, kick sugar cravings, boost your immune system and learn new healthy eating habits  along with building your daily stress relief toolkit.
No Starvation or Gimmicky Tonics- You will Eat Delicious Whole Foods.

*Note: Once you have paid, I will send an email with all your program materials as well as invite you to the private facebook group forum.  All of your materials will be on the facebook forum as well, just to make things even easier :)

name: Personal Shopping Day
description:
Wardrobe Therapist
6 hour full day of shopping
Complimentary 30 minute phone consultation 
You will have my full support and experience with fit and form so trying on clothing will not be stressful.
Together we will choose looks that fit your vision and your budget.

name: Closet Edit
description:
2 hour consultation
I will help you organize your current wardrobe.  No need to rush out and spend money on more clothing just yet.

With your input, we will define your personal style!...
